$interpreted: Sanchez: Shut up, will you!? You're disturbing my sleep!
Rune: ...Noise.
Sanchez: What noise? You're the only one making noise.
Sanchez: Who's making all that noise!?
Rune: So many...dead bodies.
Sanchez: Master Yusuf!!
Disciple: Well, what do you think is the appropriate course of action?
Yusuf: I...I know I've been greedy. I shouldn't have been secretly selling the medicine. But we've been helping the sect! Please don't kill me!
Disciple: You know too much.
Rune: Slaves must...protect their master...!
Disciple: Hmph! You'd best repent before you meet your maker...With Sdorica present, please grant me the...
Rune: ...danger...
Sanchez: Hey! Who told you to hide here! Don't you get me in trouble!
Patrol Captain: Who dares disturb the Priest's residence!?
Patrol Captain: What in the hell happened!?
Sanchez: Thank heavens you've come!
Patrol Captain: Priest Yusuf!? What the...
Patrol Captain: No signs of a struggle. Must be somebody close to...
Patrol Captain: Are you——
Sanchez: ——there were people wearing purple clothes! They were just here! I've never seen them before!
Patrol Captain: Priest Yusuf's residence is heavily protected. There's no way a group of strangers got in. But you...
Sanchez: Really! It wasn't me, I didn't do anything!
Patrol Captain: These two slaves murdered their own master! There's no pardon for such a crime! Lock them up!
Sanchez: Wait, please! You're mistaken! We're not the ones who murdered our master!
